{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding the AI products that have been introduced in the area of waste classification recycling.",
    "[43] developed an enhanced YOLO model to automate the detection of garbage, with a focus on addressing river pollution caused by urbanization.",
    "Their method attained a remarkable 89% mean average accuracy (mAP) in identifying floating trash, such as plastic bottles and aluminum cans, even under difficult circumstances such as fluctuating illumination and different backdrops.",
    "[7] investigated the efficacy of YOLOv8, the most recent version of YOLO object identification models, in automating trash sorting.",
    "The objective was to improve the effectiveness and safety of waste treatment procedures."
  ]
}